		<td width="550" align="left" valign="top" style="font-family:'Century Gothic',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:18px;line-height:22px;color:#00aeef"><strong>A MESSAGE FROM OUR CEO</strong></td>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		</tr>
		
		<tr>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		<td width="550" align="center" valign="top"><img src="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/images/staffing/Images/ncstc_hr_290914.jpg" width="550" height="22" border="0" style="display:block"></td>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		</tr>
		
		<tr>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		<td width="550" align="left" valign="top" style="font-family:'Century Gothic',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:20px;color:#222222">
		
			<table width="550" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"><tbody><tr>
			
			<td align="left" valign="top"><p>Dear all,</p>
			
			<p>As Christmas approaches, I wanted to take a moment to write and thank you all, our seasonal staff, for your terrific work with The Challenge this year.  It is no overstatement to say that our programmes simply would not happen without your contribution, excellence and dedication. On behalf of the entire organisation and the young people with whom we work, I am immensely grateful to you all.</p>
			
			<p>I wish you and your families a very happy Christmas and a peaceful New Year.</p>
			
			<p>Yours sincerely,<br><br>
			<img src="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/images/staffing/Images/oliver-lee-signature.gif" alt="" width="200" height="86" border="0"></p>
			
			<p>Oliver Lee OBE<br>
			Chief Executive<br>
			The Challenge</p></td>
			
			<td align="right" valign="top"><img src="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/images/staffing/Images/oliver-lee-portrait.jpg" alt="" width="225" height="200" border="0"></td>
			
			</tr></tbody></table>
		</td>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		</tr>
		
		<tr>
		
		<td width="600" height="50" colspan="3" align="center" valign="top"></td>
		
		</tr>
		
		<tr>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		<td width="550" align="left" valign="top" style="font-family:'Century Gothic',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:18px;line-height:22px;color:#ea007a"><strong>APPLICATIONS FOR 2015 NOW OPEN</strong></td>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		</tr>
		
		<tr>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		<td width="550" align="center" valign="top"><img src="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/images/staffing/Images/ncstc_hr_290914.jpg" width="550" height="22" border="0" style="display:block"></td>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		</tr>
		
		<tr>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		<td width="550" align="left" valign="top" style="font-family:'Century Gothic',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:20px;color:#222222">
		
			<table width="550" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"><tbody><tr>
			
			<td align="left" valign="top"><p>In 2014, 19,500 young people gained a life-changing on NCS and we couldn’t have done it without the 3,000 seasonal staff. 
</p>
<b> New locations for 2015!</b> <br>
The Challenge is set to grow even more next year and we will also be delivering NCS in new locations including Buckinghamshire and Berkshire. So why not come and share your knowledge, skills and experience which made 2014 such a success with us again in 2015?</p>
</p>
<b> Returning Alumni</b> <br>We will be contacting all our Alumni with more details on applications for 2015.&nbsp; Information about your feedback will be sent out in early January.</p>
			
			<p>If you are interested in working with us again, please submit your application in the new year. The earlier you apply, the greater your choice of available locations and dates.</p>
			
			<p>Submitting an application is now even easier for returning staff. Our Staffing Website remembers your previous application so you simply need to refresh any relevant fields.</p>
			
			<p>Start your 2015 application <a href="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/Login.aspx?ReturnUrl=%2fsecure%2f" target="_blank">here</a></p>
			
			<p>We have 3,500 roles available so do recommend the programme to any friends or colleagues who may be interested!</p></td>
			
			<td align="right" valign="top"><img src="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/images/photos/ncstc_staff-rightsideimg-comm1_211014.jpg" alt="" width="225" height="200" border="0"><br>
			<img src="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/images/photos/ncstc_staff-rightsideimg-group1_211014.jpg" alt="" width="225" height="200" border="0"><br>
			<img src="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/images/photos/ncstc_staff-sideimg-actv1_211014.jpg" alt="" width="225" height="270" border="0"></td>
			
			</tr></tbody></table>
		</td>
		
