			<table width="550" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"><tbody><tr>
			
			<td align="left" valign="top"><p>A big thank you to everyone who gave us feedback on their NCS experience. This feedback has been incorporated into our annual review and will make 2015 even better!</p>
<p> <b>And the winners are....</b><br> All staff who submitted feedback were entered into a prize draw for the chance to win one of four £25 Amazon vouchers. The lucky winners were picked by the Staffing Team’s ‘Human Fruit Machine’. The winners were <b><br> Emma Tovey (South London) <br> Chris Bowie (South London) <br> Helen Longridge (North-West England) <br> Reena Silva (West London).<b/></p>
			
			<p><strong>Congratulations to our winners.</strong></p></td>
			
			<td align="right" valign="top"><img src="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/images/photos/ncstc_staff-sideimg-skill3_211014.jpg" alt="" width="225" height="270" border="0"></td>
			
			</tr></tbody></table>
		</td>
		
