		<td width="550" align="left" valign="top" style="font-family:'Century Gothic',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:20px;color:#222222">
		
			<table width="550" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"><tbody><tr>
			
			<td align="left" valign="top"><p><strong>Camp Leaders</strong><br>
			Spend summer 2015 living and working in the States at a traditional American summer camp. You can grab yourself a paid 9-week job working with kids in America, then go traveling for up to a month afterwards. With <a href="http://www.campleaders.com/gb/?gclid=COnM8oP9z8ICFaHKtAodFmgAbA" target="_blank">Camp Leaders</a>, you get return transatlantic flights, food and accommodation provided by your camp, 90 days’ medical insurance, assistance with visas, application and paperwork and up to $1150 pocket money, all from only £399.</p></td>
			
			<td align="right" valign="top"><img src="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/images/staffing/Images/camp-leaders-pic.jpg" alt="" width="225" height="200" border="0"><br>
			<img src="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/images/staffing/Images/camp-leaders-logo.gif" alt="" width="225" height="70" border="0"></td>
			
			</tr></tbody></table>
		</td>
		
